{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c9a4a790de","title":"中央转发察哈尔省关于取缔一贯道的情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"21e53aefde","index":0,"year":1951,"month":2,"day":21,"articleId":"c9a4a790de"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"05cf6c9450","type":"title","text":"中央转发察哈尔省关于取缔一贯道的情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c9a4a790de"},{"id":"d402be3d8a","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c9a4a790de"},{"id":"a46d3a47e6","type":"appellation","text":"各中央局，并转分局及各省市区党委：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c9a4a790de"},{"id":"0aecde3616","type":"paragraph","text":"消灭一贯道，第一要有充分准备，同时动作，方能一网打尽；第二要布置展览会，向群众作宣传工作。这两点是和消灭国民党特务组织时所应采的办法大体相同。除山西消灭一贯道的经验已通报你们外，现又有察哈尔一个成功的经验，值得参考。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c9a4a790de"},{"id":"f5dc769f4c","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央二月廿一日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c9a4a790de"}],"page":{"id":"0102af4fd4","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c9a4a790de","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"cfc3e29b52","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"c9a4a790de","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央华北局1951年2月20日给中央并各省委、京津两市委的电报中总结的察哈尔省取缔一贯道的经验。他们的主要做法是：1950年11月至1951年2月5日，全省各地对一贯道道首统一进行搜捕。在搜捕前后，广泛地进行宣传教育工作，利用各种形式（报纸、电台、漫画、展览会、诉苦会、群众会、公审会等），揭穿一贯道的反革命罪行，提高干部群众的政治水平。目前各地正集中力量进行甄别审讯，追捕漏网道首，号召退道，控诉道头，进行揭发宣传，以扩大战果。"},{"id":"d7d765c6c9","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"c9a4a790de","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共山西省委1951年1月9日关于取缔一贯道的情况给华北局并报中央的报告。"}],"contents":[{"id":"120f0bd6da","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"c9a4a790de"},{"id":"8436d5cac7","type":"paragraph","text":"二月廿一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"c9a4a790de"},{"id":"8e2b02e7ab","type":"title","text":"中央转发察哈尔省关于取缔一贯道的情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"c9a4a790de"},{"id":"cfc3e29b52","type":"paragraph","text":"消灭一贯道，第一要有充分准备，同时动作，方能一网打尽；第二要布置展览会，向群众作宣传工作。这两点是和消灭国民觉特务组织时所应采的办法大体相同。除山西消灭一贯道的经验\"已通报你们外，现又有察哈尔一个成功的经验，值得参考。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"c9a4a790de"},{"id":"d7d765c6c9","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局，并转分局及各省市区党委","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"c9a4a790de"}],"page":{"id":"de4487f08b","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"c9a4a790de","start":131,"end":131}}}},"__N_SSG":true}